<p>MOVIE: &#8220;<strong><a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0814314/synopsis">Seven Pounds</a></strong>&#8220;, featuring Will Smith, Woody Harrelson, Rosario Dawson. A dramatic tale of redemption centered around multiple organ donations.</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://modern-injustice.com/2011/12/08/fact-organ-trafficking-is-on-the-rise/">Fact: Organ Trafficking Is On The Rise</a></strong>, latest facts from Modern Injustice, 12/08/11</p>
<p><strong><a href="http://communities.washingtontimes.com/neighborhood/rights-so-divine/2012/jan/17/worst-form-human-trafficking/">The worst form of human trafficking</a></strong>, Â The Washington Times,Â JanuaryÂ 17, 2011</p>
